snippet.title: Intelligence II #15 - VC 4000
snippet.description: This is the second and last in my collection of braintwisters for the Interton VC 4000. This time it's a digital version of four-in-a-row. The AI is pretty easy on the lowest levels, but it can get harder. You also have the option of two player modes. If you have a keen eye - you can see the CPU should have won at 5:28. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/08/intelligence-ii-15-vc-4000.html
